Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.42,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,受到東南亞金融危機的影響  股價暴跌之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.16,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然股票市場看來暫時有所回復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.90,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,但有人隨機向全國銀行賬戶匯入數萬億日元  引起了騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.45,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,同時物價的急劇上升導致日元市價…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一美元換三千日元?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了  快給我兌換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些店只用美元賣東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.22,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This movement of the Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.22,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,這次日元的動盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.18,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,is irrelevant to {\i1}C{\r}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.18,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,和「C」沒有關係吧  是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:28.05,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:28.05,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.14,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It is sort of conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.14,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,那是由於某種陰謀而導致的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:31.93,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What about 「C」?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:31.93,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,那「C」的情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.27,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.27,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:50.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世間的人還真是單純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.13,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道總有一天事情會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.69,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:04.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我總感覺只是一場必須獲勝的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.54,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,或許如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:10.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:11.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,到結算還有一小時的時間


Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.24,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Open Deal」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.41,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Sleeping Beauty Micro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  Micro Flation  五千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,十億!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:18.82,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:23.67,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:24.96,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公縻!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.06,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Trade」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mezzo Flation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.53,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「EBO」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:44.65,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你說不能兌換了  是怎麼回事?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,各國已經停止使用日元交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界最堅挺的貨幣化為廢紙  沒想到真有這麼一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.40,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1217,181)}遠東金融街的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.60,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.85,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:27.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.37,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Macro… Mezzo… Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,傑魯傑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真危險  真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也糟糕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也會糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:58.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  我還希望你能繼承我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:03.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼我都希望這一刻能成為永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾堅信著我們能同享這一價值觀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看法不同罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,目的是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是時機已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公縻  只能用Macro了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想… 用Macro出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,全力… 我想全力應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.22,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Macro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.47,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Economic Blockade」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.10,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Overheated Economy」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不能動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:48.99,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,受金融廳的命令在全國實行的禁止外幣兌換措施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.78,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,導致各地情況幾近於暴亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有妹妹  也遭遇了相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:55.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會贊同我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.00,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,令妹真的希望這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是為了自己而這麼做不是嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼是為了現在  為了弱者而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,結果  不都是為了一己之利嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,少自以為是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你說不是美元就不能購買是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.19,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1217,157)}首都內某處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那不只是謠言而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是謠言  但這是總店的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不能收取日元出售貨品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  Charge!10億!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.93,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說我們Asset就是Entre的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要為了公縻而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:53.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是公縻卻在為了我而戰鬥  這樣不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻覺得  這樣反而能讓我感到安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次和妹妹對話的時候  妹妹這麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「如果今天能一直延續就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「像這樣毫無改變的每一天能夠永遠持續就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無法感受明日的妹妹  這是鐫刻在她血肉之中的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以說「現在對我來說最重要」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:23.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,子欲養而親不在  人本來就應該珍視憐惜眼前的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:28.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,而不應杞人憂天  去為難以捉摸的未來操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  異變就在我眼前發生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要珍惜身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不暗中操作  一切都會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的行動能讓人獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:47.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若再沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被拯救又有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹真正想說的是「不對」不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對你自己所說過的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看了首相的會面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,政府也真是使出了吃奶的勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有人相信政府所說的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你會離開日本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的傢伙已經離開日本了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三國先生說他有個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能再醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorched Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.15,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Cannibalization」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.74,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Macro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorched…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.74,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Economic Blockade」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.99,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Cannibalization」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你和她妹妹一摸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三國先生正在做的事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吸取你的血來給「你」輸血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,區區Asset敢對我說教?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,和他相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還敢繼續說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然討厭和他分離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也會這麼戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,為了他而戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你為了什麼而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了三國先生而戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那三國先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是為了你而戰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  找的零錢裡頭有玩具錢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你這漆黑的錢是什麼東西啊

Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無論我怎麼做  無論你怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,人類早晚都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:00.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  每天我都當成人生的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,拼盡全力活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,明天會是怎麼樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已  僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天比昨天還要悲慘  那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.40,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣明天依然會到來!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q  吃掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉這個Entre
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,貴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.55,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.72,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,夢醒的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.46,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,C's chain reaction is about to hit Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.46,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,「C」連鎖到達日本了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:13.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三國壯一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下也好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已經戰鬥的足夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,貴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥最近很像爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也有想要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是和哥哥一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很像爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣  那至今為止我做的那些又算是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,貴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,貴子  貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,貴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.50,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The chain action passed though Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.50,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,「C」連鎖已經通過了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world can that be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,…怎麼可能這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,日元失去價值的話  Midas Money也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,於是「C」的連鎖好像已經通過日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遠東金融街遲早會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在Deal中呢  這可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三國先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,給我反轉印鈔機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不會後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那做你所想做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,謹遵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把未來買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,尊意!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.09,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「You have control」\N您獲得控制權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看來要分別了  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  今後不再為你而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,去本該去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果還能在你的身邊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不對  貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會說… 要分別?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三十倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:14:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我覺得  差不多是平時的四十倍那樣喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,遇見你  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱… 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在未來相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要永遠停留在這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為無論什麼事  信用都是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到金融街的信用這麼簡單就失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道什麼時候會發生什麼樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你對金融街的依賴看來是比想像中更厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還是逃不掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這不正說明你備受信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是不能再偏袒你的任性了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對於什麼是正確的  什麼是錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很迷茫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有正確的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是為了讓世界變得更美好而戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且世界的確變得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  金融街是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有了它  你們才會相遇  戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,世間萬物皆有其存在意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,無論它有多邪惡東西  無論它有多悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,必定都有把人類引向更好道路上的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去的世界已經完全變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你  還有你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,得回了非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:21.02,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,（背景為復利公式。）
Comment: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Epilogue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,球跑到那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一共是七美元三十美分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,七美元三十美分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,正好不用找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,快點  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來比較危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,健治小朋友  不能插隊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家有沒有好好跟著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,羽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗? 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看到與曾經喜歡的女生極為相像的保育員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「說不定她也在某個地方得回了幸福未來吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你正沉浸在這樣的感慨中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你實在是過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你取回來的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說  未來便是抵押
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,未來存在的地方  我也一樣存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:07.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,金融街是不會毀滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:09.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:10.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用於抵押的未來比起原來可是多得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:20.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有這個意願的話  可以隨時叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,當時有笑一笑就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,…向著那未來

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.47,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄從窗子逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.72,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.31,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,化為RPG遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:05.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,沿著箭頭的方向  我被帶入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,一個五光十色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.03,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,響起開始的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:17.03,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,全身為愛煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.00,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,想要見到你和你的未來  我披荊斬棘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:23.16,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,穿越黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.92,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.63,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,就算來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.01,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,就算必須乾坤一擲  也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.47,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我愛上你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.64,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要迷上你  還有你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,即使欺騙全世界也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.52,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就拉起我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.82,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是AB選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.48,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能用道理說清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.45,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,比起全世界的未解之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:20:04.83,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}我更想知道你的未來  你的心

